entries.s_10: The quarantine zone is a restricted area, citizen.
entries.s_14: What? Let me see your authorization code.
entries.s_18: Ah yes, %TU, I didn't expect to see you again. Well, not alive that is.  Do you want to enter the quarantine zone?
entries.s_19: Well, I see. Everything checks out. I can't say that I envy you, but I certainly appreciate what you are doing for the Empire...whatever you are doing.
entries.s_21: I hear you received the anti-virus. I personally wouldn't trust anything created in the quarantine zone...but you seem to be fine. I hope it lasts, for your sake...
entries.s_27: I heard that you found a contingent of Imperial Stormtroopers in the original research center. This is going to be great for recruitment!
entries.s_30: Sorry citizen.This is a quarantined area. Please keep moving.
